			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Private letter from Filipe de Sousa, religious, to Gaspar de Brito, attorney of the archbishop of Braga.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author talks to his friend about his business and the payment of the vows.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">This case was about the payment of vows, in the form of 28 bushels of rye, at the village of Outeiro, near Braga. The attorney Gaspar de Brito alleged that this payment should be done by all the dwellers of the village.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
